1品牌建構與營銷管理能力( Branding & marketing management Competency )15%2品牌策略與商務模式能力（Strategic Branding & business modeling Competency )15%3時尚行銷與公關運作能力（Fashion Marketing＆Communication Competency )15%4市場導向的產品開發、設計能力（Marketing Driven Product Development＆ Design Competency )15%5激發創新與思維力 ( Inspires Innovations and Critical Thinking)15%6強化視像表現（visual presentations)溝通技巧 (Strengthening Visual Communication Skills)15%7美學人文力 (Development Aesthetics and Liberal Arts)10%





